  ‚àÄ ‚¶ÉœÑ : TripLength‚¶Ñ, 0 < œÑ ‚Üí (œÑ ‚àà œÉ ‚Üî c < w œÑ / œÑ)

/--
Theorem 1 partial-threshold policy: it contains every trip with rate strictly
