arbitrary subset of the boundary `w(œÑ)/œÑ = c`.
-/
def partialThresholdRatePolicy (w : PricingFunction) (c : ‚Ñù) (œÉ : TripPolicy) : Prop :=
  ‚àÄ ‚¶ÉœÑ : TripLength‚¶Ñ, 0 < œÑ ‚Üí
    (c < w œÑ / œÑ ‚Üí œÑ ‚àà œÉ) ‚àß (œÑ ‚àà œÉ ‚Üí c ‚â§ w œÑ / œÑ)

/-- Canonical strict-threshold set, accepting trips with rate strictly above `c`. -/
