    Œº arrivalRate w œÉ added hdisjoint hadded_measurable hw_integrable_œÉ
    hw_integrable_added htime_integrable_œÉ htime_integrable_added
    hlambda htime_nonneg hadded_time_pos
    (le_singleStateAverageTripRate_of_pointwise_le
      Œº w added (singleStateRenewalReward Œº arrivalRate w œÉ)
