      0 ‚â§ singleStateTripTime Œº œÉ - singleStateTripTime Œº boundary)
    (hboundary_time_pos : 0 < singleStateTripTime Œº boundary)
    (hboundary_positive : boundary ‚äÜ acceptAllPolicy)
