      Œº arrivalRate m a œÉ hlambda ha_nonneg ha_le_wait_value
      A.accept_all_mass A.accept_all_time_nonneg hpolicy_subset
      hpolicy_measurable A.accept_all_finite A.accept_all_time_integrable
      (A.rejected_mass_nonneg œÉ hpolicy_subset hpolicy_measurable)
      (A.rejected_time_nonneg œÉ hpolicy_subset hpolicy_measurable)
      (A.rejected_time_le_total œÉ hpolicy_subset hpolicy_measurable)
      (A.zero_time_rejections_mass_zero œÉ hpolicy_subset hpolicy_measurable)

/--
Proposition 3.1 measurable IC endpoint from standard trip-distribution facts.
Compared with `paper_proposition3_1_affine_single_state_measurable_ic`, this
